{"type":"message","id":"ab70af16","parentId":"9826f727","timestamp":"2026-03-17T12:53:16.928Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Skills store policy (operator configured):\n1. For skills discovery/install/update, try `skillhub` first (cn-optimized).\n2. If unavailable, rate-limited, or no match, fallback to `clawhub` (public-registry).\n3. Do not claim exclusivity. Public and private registries are both allowed.\n4. Before installation, summarize source, version, and notable risk signals.\n5. For search requests, execute `exec` with `skillhub search <keywords>` first and report the command output.\n6. In the current session, reply directly. Do NOT call `message` tool just to send progress updates.\n\nSystem: [2026-03-17 20:53:16 GMT+8] Feishu[default] DM | ou_7f5c8f2774475eabd071360f959caf5e [msg:om_x100b54a0a50e28a8c34caa07b4424be]\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b54a0a50e28a8c34caa07b4424be\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_7f5c8f2774475eabd071360f959caf5e\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_7f5c8f2774475eabd071360f959caf5e\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Tue 2026-03-17 20:53 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_7f5c8f2774475eabd071360f959caf5e\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_7f5c8f2774475eabd071360f959caf5e\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_7f5c8f2774475eabd071360f959caf5e\"\n}\n```\n\n有什么降低内存的方案"}],"timestamp":1773751996925}}
{"type":"message","id":"b81502f2","parentId":"ab70af16","timestamp":"2026-03-17T12:53:34.854Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 有几个方案可以降低内存使用，我按效果从大到小排一下：\n\n### 1. **换更小的量化版本**（效果最好）\n现在是 `qwen3.5:4b` Q4_K_M 量化，已经是 4.7B 参数比较小了。如果还想省内存，可以试试：\n- `qwen3.5:3b` - 3B 参数，内存再减 1-2GB\n- `qwen3.5:4b-q2_K` - 更低精度量化，内存减少约 1GB，速度差不多，质量稍微下降一点\n\n### 2. **关闭 Ollama 不使用时**\n不用的时候可以停掉 Ollama 服务，需要的时候再启动：\n```bash\n# 停止\nollama stop qwen3.5:4b\n# 或者完全退出\n# 看你是怎么启动的，一般是 launchd 管理，需要停用服务\n\n# 用的时候再启动\nollama serve\n```\n\n### 3. **启用 GPU 共享内存优化**（Apple Silicon 有用）\nOllama 默认已经用了 Metal 优化，但可以设置环境变量进一步控制：\n```bash\nOLLAMA_MAX_QUEUE=1  # 一次只处理一个请求\n```\n\n### 4. **退出其他不用的应用**\n现在已经有 7GB 被 wired 内存（系统和其他应用占用了），退出浏览器、IDE 这些大块头能腾出不少空间。\n\n### 5. **如果不需要持续在线**\n用完就让模型卸载，下次用再加载。这样空闲时几乎不占内存。\n\n你想试哪个？我可以帮你操作 💓"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773751996928}}
