{"type":"message","id":"044a4280","parentId":"aa70d842","timestamp":"2026-03-17T12:55:33.510Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 找到了，排在 ollama 之后的内存大户：\n\n| 应用 | 内存占用 |\n|------|----------|\n| **ollama (qwen3.5:4b)** | **5715MB (5.7GB)** |\n| WindowServer (系统界面) | 663MB |\n| OpenClaw gateway (node) | 489MB |\n| WebKit (Safari浏览器) | ~342MB+ |\n| Opencode | 330MB |\n| Feishu (飞书整体) | ~185MB + 多个助手进程 ≈ 600MB+ |\n| Safari | 189MB |\n\n所以主要就是 **ollama 占了 5.7GB**，这是最大头。其次是系统和浏览器、飞书这些加起来也有 1.5GB 左右。\n\n**要降内存最有效的就是：**\n1. 换更小的模型（比如 3B 参数版本能省 1-2GB）\n2. 不用的时候把 ollama 停掉，能直接释放 5.7GB\n\n你想怎么处理？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773752121461}}
