{"type":"message","id":"e47495b9","parentId":"6ca5f655","timestamp":"2026-03-17T12:56:31.610Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] Ollama 启动挺快的，几秒钟就好了。加载模型也就几秒钟到十几秒，取决于模型大小。\n\n但是频繁启停其实也不太方便，如果不常用的话倒是可以用完就停，要用再启。你是打算一直保持运行还是用的时候再开？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773752186902}}
