{"type":"message","id":"f9948353","parentId":"b3cea49d","timestamp":"2026-03-17T13:14:46.512Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 现在排在 ollama 之后的内存大户：\n\n| 进程 | 内存 | 说明 | 是否可以退出 |\n|------|------|------|-------------|\n| **ollama** | **5735MB** | qwen3.5:4b 模型 | - |\n| OpenClaw gateway (node) | 511MB | 核心进程，不能退 | ❌ |\n| .opencode | 331MB | Opcode 编辑器 | 如果现在不用可以退 | ✅ |\n| VTDecoderXPCServ | 239MB | 视频解码，系统进程 | 不用动 | ❌ |\n| Lark Helper (飞书多个助手进程) | ~221MB + 216MB + ... ≈ 500MB+ | 飞书现在就在用，退了会影响聊天 | ❌ |\n| WallpaperDynamic | 200MB | 动态壁纸 | 如果不需要可以退 | ✅ |\n\n可以退出 opencode 和动态壁纸来再腾出 ~500MB 内存，你要我帮你退吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773753276806}}
{"type":"message","id":"625f2a99","parentId":"f9948353","timestamp":"2026-03-17T13:24:25.120Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Skills store policy (operator configured):\n1. For skills discovery/install/update, try `skillhub` first (cn-optimized).\n2. If unavailable, rate-limited, or no match, fallback to `clawhub` (public-registry).\n3. Do not claim exclusivity. Public and private registries are both allowed.\n4. Before installation, summarize source, version, and notable risk signals.\n5. For search requests, execute `exec` with `skillhub search <keywords>` first and report the command output.\n6. In the current session, reply directly. Do NOT call `message` tool just to send progress updates.\n\nSystem: [2026-03-17 21:24:24 GMT+8] Feishu[default] DM | ou_7f5c8f2774475eabd071360f959caf5e [msg:om_x100b54a12eb864b4c109081b489fa02]\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b54a12eb864b4c109081b489fa02\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_7f5c8f2774475eabd071360f959caf5e\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_7f5c8f2774475eabd071360f959caf5e\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Tue 2026-03-17 21:24 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_7f5c8f2774475eabd071360f959caf5e\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_7f5c8f2774475eabd071360f959caf5e\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_7f5c8f2774475eabd071360f959caf5e\"\n}\n```\n\n还有其他站内存的么16不应该还有10g么"}],"timestamp":1773753865117}}
{"type":"message","id":"2d994918","parentId":"625f2a99","timestamp":"2026-03-17T13:24:41.153Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 你说的对，16G内存为什么显示 15G 用完了还剩几百MB空闲，这其实是 macOS 的内存管理方式：\n\n**macOS 会把很多内存用作：**\n- **Wired 内存**：7GB 左右（核心系统、缓存、共享库）\n- **Compressed 内存**：2GB 左右（把不常用的内存压缩节省空间）\n- **Shared 内存**：多个进程共享的动态库，6GB 左右\n\n所以实际上你看到的 \"15GB used\" 包含了很多系统复用的共享内存，并不是真的都被应用占用了。**真正给用户应用用的空闲还有几百MB到1GB左右**，这在 macOS 上是正常现象。\n\n让我再给你看看完整排行：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_gutm7i7fyzhv5wpqtffyw0jb","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"top -o rsize -l 1 | grep \"liyue\" | awk '{print $10 \"\\t\" $2}' | head -15","timeout":5}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773753865119}}
