{"type":"message","id":"3fff723c","parentId":"7e80be0a","timestamp":"2026-03-17T13:24:55.583Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 除了 ollama 的 5.7GB，用户空间的应用占用大概是这样：\n\n- **ollama**: 5.7GB\n- **OpenClaw (node)**: 511MB\n- **.opencode**: 331MB\n- **飞书整体 (多个进程)**: ~600MB\n- **WallpaperDynamic**: 200MB\n- **其他零碎加起来**: ~300MB\n\n总共用户应用占用大概 **7.6GB** 左右，剩下的 7-8GB 被系统占用了（wired + 共享缓存 + 压缩），这在 macOS 上是正常的。\n\n**剩下能腾出来的空间不多了**，主要就是 opencode 的 331MB 和壁纸的 200MB，退了能再腾出 500MB 左右空闲。要不要退？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773753881379}}
