{"type":"message","id":"74cdcbe3","parentId":"6699a1ec","timestamp":"2026-03-17T14:33:21.838Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_n73gf4q3wbb7lxl1z9mtwssr","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"You can use \"skillhub install [skill]\" to install.\nword  Word\n  - Control Word app sessions, documents, selections, comments, export, and review state with osascript workflows.\nControl Word app sessions, documents, selections, comments, export, and review state with osascript workflows.\n  - version: 1.0.0\nword-docx  Word / DOCX\n  - Create, inspect, and edit Microsoft Word documents and DOCX files with reliable styles, numbering, tracked changes, tables, sections, and compatibility check...\n创建、检查和编辑 Word/DOCX 文档，支持样式、编号、修订追踪、表格、分节及兼容性检查。\n  - version: 1.0.2\nwordpress-api  WordPress\n  - WordPress.com API integration with managed OAuth. Manage posts, pages, sites, and content.\nUse this skill when users want to create, read, update, or delete WordPress.com posts, pages, or manage site content.\nFor other third party apps, use the api-gateway skill (https://clawhub.ai/byungkyu/api-gateway).\nRequires network access and valid Maton API key.\nWordPress.com API集成，支持托管OAuth认证。管理文章、页面及网站内容，支持增删改查操作。其他第三方应用请使用api-gateway技能。需要网络连接和有效的Maton API密钥。\n  - version: 1.0.1\nwordpress  Wordpress REST API\n  - OpenClaw skill that provides a WordPress REST API CLI for posts, pages, categories, tags, users, and custom requests using plain HTTP.\nOpenClaw 技能，提供 WordPress REST API 命令行工具，支持文章、页面、分类、标签、用户及自定义 HTTP 请求。\n  - version: 1.0.0\nwordpress-pro  Wordpress Pro\n  - Use when developing WordPress themes, plugins, customizing Gutenberg blocks, implementing WooCommerce features, or optimizing WordPress performance and security.\n适用于WordPress主题插件开发、古腾堡区块定制、WooCommerce功能实现及性能安全优化。\n  - version: 0.1.0\nwordpress-api-gutenberg  Wopdpress AI Blogger\n  - Create, edit, and publish WordPress posts via REST API with full Gutenberg block support. Use when Codex needs to automate WordPress content publishing, gene...\nCreate, edit, and publish WordPress posts via REST API with full Gutenberg block support. Use when Codex needs to automate WordPress content publishing, gene...\n  - version: 1.0.0\nwordpress-rest-api  WordPress REST API\n  - Work with the WordPress REST API for route discovery, authentication, reads and writes, core endpoint selection, and custom namespace inspection. Use when a...\nWork with the WordPress REST API for route discovery, authentication, reads and writes, core endpoint selection, and custom namespace inspection. Use when a...\n  - version: 0.6.0\nwordpress-wp-cli-admin  WordPress WP-CLI Admin\n  - Operate WordPress installs through WP-CLI for inspection, core maintenance, plugin and theme management, users, options, content, media, cron, database tasks...\nOperate WordPress installs through WP-CLI for inspection, core maintenance, plugin and theme management, users, options, content, media, cron, database tasks...\n  - version: 0.5.0\ntiangong-wps-word-automation  Word Automation\n  - Automate common Word/WPS document operations on Windows via COM (read text, replace, insert, headings, headers/footers, page breaks, merge, split, export to PDF/TXT, add/replace images). Use for single-document actions (no batch).\n通过 Windows COM 接口自动化 Word/WPS 文档操作（读取文本、替换、插入、标题、页眉页脚、分页、合并、拆分、导出 PDF/TXT、添加/替换图片），仅适用于单文档（非批量）。\n  - version: 0.1.0\nword-document-organizer  word-document-organizer\n  - 智能整理Word文档，自动格式化、生成目录、统一样式，支持学术/商务/极简模板\n智能整理Word文档，自动格式化、生成目录、统一样式，支持学术/商务/极简模板\n  - version: 1.0.1\nwordpress-remote-news-publisher  WordPress Remote News Publisher\n  - Automates news article creation and publishing to remote WordPress via SSH and WP-CLI, including image handling and SEO metadata integration.\nAutomates news article creation and publishing to remote WordPress via SSH and WP-CLI, including image handling and SEO metadata integration.\n  - version: 1.0.0\nwordpress-wp-cli-internal-api  WordPress WP-CLI Internal API\n  - Build, inspect, and extend WP-CLI command code using the documented stable internal API. Use when the task involves custom WP-CLI commands, package bootstrap...\nBuild, inspect, and extend WP-CLI command code using the documented stable internal API. Use when the task involves custom WP-CLI commands, package bootstrap...\n  - version: 0.5.0\n1password  1password\n  - Set up and use 1Password CLI (op). Use when installing the CLI, enabling desktop app integration, signing in (single or multi-account), or reading/injecting/running secrets via op.\n配置和使用 1Password CLI (op)。用于安装 CLI、启用桌面应用集成、登录（单/多账户）及通过 op 读取/注入/运行密钥。\n  - version: 1.0.1\nword-cn-format  中文word文档通用格式标准化\n  - 提供Word文档中文格式标准化功能，统一标题、正文、图片和图表格式，确保符合中文排版规范。\n提供Word文档中文格式标准化功能，统一标题、正文、图片和图表格式，确保符合中文排版规范。\n  - version: 1.0.0\nword-format  Government Word Format Standardizer\n  - Convert uploaded Word documents (.docx) into the fixed Chinese official-document format defined by the bundled government-style template bundle. Use when Cod...\nConvert uploaded Word documents (.docx) into the fixed Chinese official-document format defined by the bundled government-style template bundle. Use when Cod...\n  - version: 1.0.0\nhumanizer  Humanizer\n  - Remove signs of AI-generated writing from text. Use when editing or reviewing\ntext to make it sound more natural and human-written. Based on Wikipedia's\ncomprehensive \"Signs of AI writing\" guide. Detects and fixes patterns including:\ninflated symbolism, promotional language, superficial -ing analyses, vague\nattributions, em dash overuse, rule of three, AI vocabulary words, negative\nparallelisms, and excessive conjunctive phrases.\n消除AI写作痕迹，使文本更自然真实。基于维基百科\"AI写作特征\"指南，识别并修正夸张象征、宣传用语、肤浅-ing分析、模糊归因、破折号滥用、三项排比、AI词汇、负面平行结构及冗长连接词等模式。\n  - version: 1.0.0\nkeyword-research  Keyword Research\n  - This skill should be used when the user asks to \"find keywords\", \"keyword research\", \"what should I write about\", \"keyword difficulty score\", \"search volume...\nThis skill should be used when the user asks to \"find keywords\", \"keyword research\", \"what should I write about\", \"keyword difficulty score\", \"search volume...\n  - version: 3.0.0\nadmapix  AdMapix\n  - Ad creative search assistant. Results displayed via api.admapix.com. Triggers on keywords like: 找素材, 搜广告, 广告视频, 创意素材, 竞品广告, ad creative, search ads, find cre...\nAd creative search assistant. Results displayed via api.admapix.com. Triggers on keywords like: 找素材, 搜广告, 广告视频, 创意素材, 竞品广告, ad creative, search ads, find cre...\n  - version: 1.0.13\nmarkdown-converter  Markdown Converter\n  - Convert documents and files to Markdown using markitdown. Use when converting PDF, Word (.docx), PowerPoint (.pptx), Excel (.xlsx, .xls), HTML, CSV, JSON, XML, images (with EXIF/OCR), audio (with transcription), ZIP archives, YouTube URLs, or EPubs to Markdown format for LLM processing or text analysis.\n使用 markitdown 将 PDF、Word(.docx)、PowerPoint(.pptx)、Excel(.xlsx/.xls)、HTML、CSV、JSON、XML、图片(含EXIF/OCR)、音频(含转录)、ZIP压缩包、YouTube链接或EPub转换为Markdown格式，便于LLM处理或文本分析。\n  - version: 1.0.0\npinch-to-post  Pinch to Post - Manage WordPress sites through WP Pinch MCP server\n  - Manage WordPress sites through WP Pinch MCP tools. Part of WP Pinch (wp-pinch.com).\n通过 WP Pinch MCP 工具管理 WordPress 网站。WP Pinch 旗下产品 (wp-pinch.com)。\n  - version: 5.5.1"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":869,"aggregated":"You can use \"skillhub install [skill]\" to install.\nword  Word\n  - Control Word app sessions, documents, selections, comments, export, and review state with osascript workflows.\nControl Word app sessions, documents, selections, comments, export, and review state with osascript workflows.\n  - version: 1.0.0\nword-docx  Word / DOCX\n  - Create, inspect, and edit Microsoft Word documents and DOCX files with reliable styles, numbering, tracked changes, tables, sections, and compatibility check...\n创建、检查和编辑 Word/DOCX 文档，支持样式、编号、修订追踪、表格、分节及兼容性检查。\n  - version: 1.0.2\nwordpress-api  WordPress\n  - WordPress.com API integration with managed OAuth. Manage posts, pages, sites, and content.\nUse this skill when users want to create, read, update, or delete WordPress.com posts, pages, or manage site content.\nFor other third party apps, use the api-gateway skill (https://clawhub.ai/byungkyu/api-gateway).\nRequires network access and valid Maton API key.\nWordPress.com API集成，支持托管OAuth认证。管理文章、页面及网站内容，支持增删改查操作。其他第三方应用请使用api-gateway技能。需要网络连接和有效的Maton API密钥。\n  - version: 1.0.1\nwordpress  Wordpress REST API\n  - OpenClaw skill that provides a WordPress REST API CLI for posts, pages, categories, tags, users, and custom requests using plain HTTP.\nOpenClaw 技能，提供 WordPress REST API 命令行工具，支持文章、页面、分类、标签、用户及自定义 HTTP 请求。\n  - version: 1.0.0\nwordpress-pro  Wordpress Pro\n  - Use when developing WordPress themes, plugins, customizing Gutenberg blocks, implementing WooCommerce features, or optimizing WordPress performance and security.\n适用于WordPress主题插件开发、古腾堡区块定制、WooCommerce功能实现及性能安全优化。\n  - version: 0.1.0\nwordpress-api-gutenberg  Wopdpress AI Blogger\n  - Create, edit, and publish WordPress posts via REST API with full Gutenberg block support. Use when Codex needs to automate WordPress content publishing, gene...\nCreate, edit, and publish WordPress posts via REST API with full Gutenberg block support. Use when Codex needs to automate WordPress content publishing, gene...\n  - version: 1.0.0\nwordpress-rest-api  WordPress REST API\n  - Work with the WordPress REST API for route discovery, authentication, reads and writes, core endpoint selection, and custom namespace inspection. Use when a...\nWork with the WordPress REST API for route discovery, authentication, reads and writes, core endpoint selection, and custom namespace inspection. Use when a...\n  - version: 0.6.0\nwordpress-wp-cli-admin  WordPress WP-CLI Admin\n  - Operate WordPress installs through WP-CLI for inspection, core maintenance, plugin and theme management, users, options, content, media, cron, database tasks...\nOperate WordPress installs through WP-CLI for inspection, core maintenance, plugin and theme management, users, options, content, media, cron, database tasks...\n  - version: 0.5.0\ntiangong-wps-word-automation  Word Automation\n  - Automate common Word/WPS document operations on Windows via COM (read text, replace, insert, headings, headers/footers, page breaks, merge, split, export to PDF/TXT, add/replace images). Use for single-document actions (no batch).\n通过 Windows COM 接口自动化 Word/WPS 文档操作（读取文本、替换、插入、标题、页眉页脚、分页、合并、拆分、导出 PDF/TXT、添加/替换图片），仅适用于单文档（非批量）。\n  - version: 0.1.0\nword-document-organizer  word-document-organizer\n  - 智能整理Word文档，自动格式化、生成目录、统一样式，支持学术/商务/极简模板\n智能整理Word文档，自动格式化、生成目录、统一样式，支持学术/商务/极简模板\n  - version: 1.0.1\nwordpress-remote-news-publisher  WordPress Remote News Publisher\n  - Automates news article creation and publishing to remote WordPress via SSH and WP-CLI, including image handling and SEO metadata integration.\nAutomates news article creation and publishing to remote WordPress via SSH and WP-CLI, including image handling and SEO metadata integration.\n  - version: 1.0.0\nwordpress-wp-cli-internal-api  WordPress WP-CLI Internal API\n  - Build, inspect, and extend WP-CLI command code using the documented stable internal API. Use when the task involves custom WP-CLI commands, package bootstrap...\nBuild, inspect, and extend WP-CLI command code using the documented stable internal API. Use when the task involves custom WP-CLI commands, package bootstrap...\n  - version: 0.5.0\n1password  1password\n  - Set up and use 1Password CLI (op). Use when installing the CLI, enabling desktop app integration, signing in (single or multi-account), or reading/injecting/running secrets via op.\n配置和使用 1Password CLI (op)。用于安装 CLI、启用桌面应用集成、登录（单/多账户）及通过 op 读取/注入/运行密钥。\n  - version: 1.0.1\nword-cn-format  中文word文档通用格式标准化\n  - 提供Word文档中文格式标准化功能，统一标题、正文、图片和图表格式，确保符合中文排版规范。\n提供Word文档中文格式标准化功能，统一标题、正文、图片和图表格式，确保符合中文排版规范。\n  - version: 1.0.0\nword-format  Government Word Format Standardizer\n  - Convert uploaded Word documents (.docx) into the fixed Chinese official-document format defined by the bundled government-style template bundle. Use when Cod...\nConvert uploaded Word documents (.docx) into the fixed Chinese official-document format defined by the bundled government-style template bundle. Use when Cod...\n  - version: 1.0.0\nhumanizer  Humanizer\n  - Remove signs of AI-generated writing from text. Use when editing or reviewing\ntext to make it sound more natural and human-written. Based on Wikipedia's\ncomprehensive \"Signs of AI writing\" guide. Detects and fixes patterns including:\ninflated symbolism, promotional language, superficial -ing analyses, vague\nattributions, em dash overuse, rule of three, AI vocabulary words, negative\nparallelisms, and excessive conjunctive phrases.\n消除AI写作痕迹，使文本更自然真实。基于维基百科\"AI写作特征\"指南，识别并修正夸张象征、宣传用语、肤浅-ing分析、模糊归因、破折号滥用、三项排比、AI词汇、负面平行结构及冗长连接词等模式。\n  - version: 1.0.0\nkeyword-research  Keyword Research\n  - This skill should be used when the user asks to \"find keywords\", \"keyword research\", \"what should I write about\", \"keyword difficulty score\", \"search volume...\nThis skill should be used when the user asks to \"find keywords\", \"keyword research\", \"what should I write about\", \"keyword difficulty score\", \"search volume...\n  - version: 3.0.0\nadmapix  AdMapix\n  - Ad creative search assistant. Results displayed via api.admapix.com. Triggers on keywords like: 找素材, 搜广告, 广告视频, 创意素材, 竞品广告, ad creative, search ads, find cre...\nAd creative search assistant. Results displayed via api.admapix.com. Triggers on keywords like: 找素材, 搜广告, 广告视频, 创意素材, 竞品广告, ad creative, search ads, find cre...\n  - version: 1.0.13\nmarkdown-converter  Markdown Converter\n  - Convert documents and files to Markdown using markitdown. Use when converting PDF, Word (.docx), PowerPoint (.pptx), Excel (.xlsx, .xls), HTML, CSV, JSON, XML, images (with EXIF/OCR), audio (w